Class FileSystemMimeMessageSender

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.communote.server.core.mail.FileSystemMimeMessageSender
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MimeMessageSender

    public class FileSystemMimeMessageSender
extends Object
implements MimeMessageSender
    MimeMessageSender which stores the message on the filesystem in a sub-directory of Communote's data directory. Mainly useful for development and tests.
    Author:
    Communote team - http://communote.github.io/
